Insider Activity


Individual




Robert J. Stanzione



Mr. Robert J. Stanzione is Chairman at ARRIS Group, Inc. and Chairman at ARRIS International Plc. He is on the Board of Directors at National Cable & Telecommunications Association.
Mr. Stanzione was previously employed as Independent Director by Symmetricom, Inc., President, Chief Operating Officer & Director by ANTEC Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Arris Interactive LLC, a Principal by AT&T Corp., and President by C-COR, Inc. He also served on the board at Georgia Cystic Fibrosis Foundation, CoaXmedia, Inc., Evolve Products, Inc., and The Cystic Fibrosis Foundation, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Clemson University and a graduate degree from North Carolina State University.



